http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#lab.value: List of United States presidential firsts

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#com.value: This list lists achievements and distinctions of various presidents of the United States. It includes distinctions achieved in their earlier life and post-presidencies. Due to some confusion surrounding sovereignty of nations during presidential visits, only nations that were independent, sovereign, or recognized by the United States during the presidency are listed here as a precedent.
